OL,6,FNewly released figures have revealed
OL,7,Fthat nearly two-thirds of Jersey's
OL,8,Fgovernment-funded schools went
OL,9,Foverbudget in 2024, leading to a
OL,10,Fcombined overspend of more than #2
OL,11,Fmillion.
OL,13,FIt comes as the number of children
OL,14,Fneeding additional support has more
OL,15,Fthan doubled since 2017, with the
OL,16,Fisland's largest teaching union
OL,17,Fbranding the situation "dire" and
OL,18,F"unsustainable".
