OL,6,FJersey's Education Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FRob Ward, says: "The reason for this
OL,8,Fis that the need is increasing.
OL,10,F"For example, records of needs have
OL,11,Fgone from 212 in 2017 to over 500 last
OL,12,Fyear and those require support: that
OL,13,Fsupport is expensive and we have to
OL,14,Fspend that money."
OL,16,FThe data from a Freedom of Information
OL,17,Frequest revealed Grainville Secondary
OL,18,FSchool had the highest overspend of
OL,19,F#553,315 in 2024, while Grouville was
OL,20,Fthe highest primary school with a
OL,21,Fdeficit of #262,964.
