OL,6,FVictoria College went overbudget by
OL,7,F#128,867 last year and has sent a
OL,8,Fletter to parents to notify them about
OL,9,Fan above-inflation 6.5% increase in
OL,10,Ffees from the Autumn term.
OL,12,FIt says the rise is necessary due to
OL,13,Fstaffing expenses and funding for
OL,14,Fpupils with Special Educational Needs,
OL,15,Fstating: "These costs are driven in
OL,16,Fpart by an increase in staff costs
OL,17,Fbased on existing delivery models and
OL,18,Finfluenced by Government of Jersey pay
OL,19,Fagreements; and in part due to an
OL,20,Fincrease in non-pay related costs of
OL,21,Frunning a school.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
