OL,6,F"Grant funding allocation from the
OL,7,FGovernment of Jersey is not
OL,8,Fsufficient. Essentially, the
OL,9,FGovernment should fund 47% of the
OL,10,Faverage cost of a pupil at another GoJ
OL,11,Fschool ` we do not believe this
OL,12,Ffunding model is currently being met.
OL,14,F"Funding for some of our pupils with
OL,15,FSpecial Educational Needs is
OL,16,Finsufficient. Some students have their
OL,17,Fsupport prorated to 47% while others
OL,18,Freceive 100%."
