OL,6,FDeputy Ward explains the budget
OL,7,Foverspends will be sorted: "The
OL,8,Fdeficits will be dealt with over the
OL,9,Fterm of the year, that's why those
OL,10,Ffigures which look good in the press
OL,11,Fare somewhat misleading.
OL,13,F"We are doing everything we can, I am
OL,14,Fan advocate for funding of schools,
OL,15,Fand we need to look into the future in
OL,16,Fwhat way we are going to meet the
OL,17,Fgrowing need across our estate.
