OL,6,F"I would always like to see the budget
OL,7,Fincreased, that's my role, I'd like us
OL,8,Fto see more opportunity to do the best
OL,9,Fthat we can for every child in this
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,F"We need an intelligent and informed
OL,13,Fdiscussion about funding, rather than
OL,14,Fconflating lots of different figures,
OL,15,Fwhich I think can be quite
OL,16,Fdisappointing for schools when one
OL,17,Fschool is paid off against another, so
OL,18,FI'd like that to end and let's have an
OL,19,Fintelligent conversation."
