OL,6,FArguing schools are not prioritised,
OL,7,FMarina Mauger from the NASUWT
OL,8,Fteachers' union says: "I just think
OL,9,Fthat if we are going to truly live on
OL,10,Fan island that puts children first,
OL,11,Fthen education should get the bulk of
OL,12,Ffunding, not the minority.
OL,14,F"The thing that is going wrong is that
OL,15,Fschools historically have been grossly
OL,16,Funderfunded by the Government.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
