OL,6,F"When I have teachers ringing me and
OL,7,Fsaying, 'We are not allowed to print,
OL,8,Fwe are not allowed to photocopy, the
OL,9,Fschool can't afford it', something is
OL,10,Fdrastically wrong to get to that place
OL,11,Fon a very wealthy island."
OL,13,FAlso commenting on the figures, Deputy
OL,14,FJonathan Renouf adds: "The minister
OL,15,Fsays that it is largely driven by an
OL,16,Fincrease in Special Educational Needs,
OL,17,Fand I think what we would like to see
OL,18,Fis a little bit of accounting to show
OL,19,Fwhere the money has actually gone and
OL,20,Fhow much of it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
